1.title: Episode #10.1
1.plot: Keith Lemon returns to present the brand new tenth series of the outrageous comedy panel show. Radio DJ and TV presenter Fearne Cotton returns as team captain following her maternity break, with fellow presenter Holly Willoughby once again leading the opposing team. Big name celebs joining the gang for the first show of the new series are boxing hero Amir Khan, The Only Way Is Essex star Lucy Mecklenburgh, Embarrassing Bodies presenter Dr Christian Jessen and Top Boy actor Ashley Walters.

2.title: Episode #10.2
2.plot: Keith Lemon presents the tenth series of the outrageous comedy panel show. Fearne Cotton recently returned as team captain following her maternity break, with fellow TV presenter Holly Willoughby once again leading the opposing team. Joining the panel for this show are former Westlife singer Brian McFadden, TV presenter Alex Jones, US singer Jason Derulo and British hip hop duo Rizzle Kicks. Who but Keith can pull off such an irreverent mixture of laugh-out-loud silliness and too-rude-for-words naughtiness?

5.title: Episode #10.5

In this bizarre dimension where everything is turned on its head, could a reversal of roles be on the cards, with the three ladies finally getting their revenge and making a fool of Keith? TOWIE's Joey Essex also guest stars - is this a world ...
